<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      rel="shortcut icon"
      href="../public/favicon.ico"
      type="image/x-icon"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../public/css/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../public/css/login.css" />
    <title>이집어때? | 로그인</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="Header__Content">
      <div class="house-header__Box">
        <div class="house-header__Titile header-login">
          <div class="house-logo">
            <a href="/"> <h1 class="reveal-text">이집어때? | 로그인</h1></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="login">
          <form action="/login" method="POST">
            <div class="title">로그인 및 회원가입</div>
            <div class="title-under">
              로그인을 통해 이집어때의 다양한 리뷰를 보여드립니다.
            </div>
            <div>
              <input
                class="input-text"
                type="email"
                placeholder="이메일을 입력해주세요"
                style="margin-bottom: 7px"
                name="userKey"
              />
              <input
                class="input-text"
                type="id"
                placeholder="아이디를 입력해주세요"
                name="userEmail"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="login-box">
              <button type="submit" class="btn-login">로그인</button>
            </div>
          </form>
          <form action="/user/signup">
            <div class="box-membership">
              <span>아직 회원이 아니신가요?</span>
              <br />
              <span
                >회원가입을 하시면 더 많은 정보와 혜택을 받으실 수
                있습니다.</span
              >
              <button class="btn-membership btn-login">회원가입</button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('footer.html') %>
  </body>
</html>
